Title: Working Girls
Writer: Lucia Aniello, Paul W. Downs, Abbi Jacobson (created by), Ilana Glazer (created by)
Actors: Abbi Jacobson, Ilana Glazer, Virginia Robinson, Elaine Hyman
Plot: Ilana tries to make some extra cash in the temp game. Abbi promises her neighbor that she will wait for his package, but when she misses the delivery, she must go to the ends of the earth to recover it.
